{"tid":2348504,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港大突殺全港唯一建築文物保護學部 主任斥黑箱作業 保育古蹟更缺人才","createTime":"2020-12-31T17:31:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T09:47:37.000Z","uid":351510,"like":12,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"779a820263e65e3d772ba37956b67023f7ce4e0d","tid":2348504,"uid":351510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T17:31:09.000Z","msg":"深水埗主教山配水庫百年建築險被毀，揭露本港古蹟保育人才不足。《蘋果》獲悉，本港現時唯一一個提供建築文物保護碩士課程的港大建築學院建築文物保護課程學部（ACP）將於明年「殺部」，明年入學的碩士學生會被併入園境建築學部，該學部將升格為學系。ACP主任李浩然確認事件，批評建築學院決定突然，事先亦無諮詢學院及港大。他曾嘗試與學院院長討論惟遭拒絕，「佢唔肯同我討論」。他批評學院「完全係黑箱作業」。<br />\n<br />\nSource 蘋果:<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201231/VZYLERDBA5CZTOQSPNST4P7PGE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201231%2FVZYLERDBA5CZTOQSPNST4P7PGE%2F&d=h8K6dYNnEA4rSgnLcindhd%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=ce2e93d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201231%2FVZYLERDBA5CZTOQSPNST4P7PGE%2F&h=1ebc0639\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201231/VZYLERDBA5CZTOQSPNST4P7PGE/</a>"},{"pid":"87086d126c2cae9595235e137534080f1b32e02f","tid":2348504,"uid":351510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T17:34:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1efef654e7fa1de50ca5ca31e43fa94ce78ddfad","tid":2348504,"uid":351510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T17:36:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"18cd6aa8ea6477dd270b4b5ca51f416ed9fea56c","tid":2348504,"uid":351510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T17:37:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"838ad72fc34a12dd7d6db63eb085317bd3ce62fa","tid":2348504,"uid":351510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T17:37:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8f9ef5467e949a7f1715206c9bdbc21c37f5cf7a","tid":2348504,"uid":351510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T17:37:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b3ae8bc